How to Accept Your Student Loan Online:
Click the Financial Aid tab, then click the Award tab, and then click Accept Award Offer by Aid Year. Select Accept, Decline or Accept a Partial Loan amount for the Federal Direct Subsidized Stafford Loan, Federal Direct Unsubsidized Loan.
