You must be enrolled at least half-time to receive Federal Direct Student Loans.
**Half-Time is defined as half of the full-time load, at least 6 hours for Undergraduates and at least 3 hours for Advanced Degrees. **
If these items are not completed in a timely manner, your loan will be canceled and will not be able to be reinstated without a written request.
